Interface Summary
Graphe This interface is the basic functionality required for implementing a graph representation

DIterator For a depth run of the graph given in argument, this iterator is in reality a class that holds a stack in order to run through the graph.
GrapheHyperbolique This class contains the representation of an hyperbolic graph.
GrapheHyperboliqueH3 This class encapsulates the computing of the positions in the hyperbolic space for a spanning tree structured graph.
